<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Minha Landing Page em Ruby</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 font-sans">

    <nav class="p-6 bg-white shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">RubyDev</div>
        <div class="space-x-4">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-red-500">Sobre</a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700">Contato</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-20 px-6 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6">
            Construa o futuro com <span class="text-red-600">Ruby</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Esta é uma landing page profissional servida pelo Sinatra. 
            Simples, rápida e elegante, como toda aplicação Ruby deve ser.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 max-w-md mx-auto">
            <form action="/contato" method="POST" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Seu nome" required 
                    class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500">
                
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="seu@email.com" required 
                    class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500">
                
                <button type="submit" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-red-700 transition">
                    Cadastrar
                </button>
            </form>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Prometemos não enviar spam!</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <footer class="py-10 border-t border-gray-200 text-center text-gray-500">
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> RubyDev - Criado iniciando no mundo Ruby.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>